text: Osinovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Polozovskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 76 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 6.5 km south-west from Polozovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Osinovka, Polozovskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai
